%% Diagram: Virtualization decision framework
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart TD
    A[Large list] --> B{Find-in-page<br/>needed?}
    B -->|Yes| C{Under<br/>~10K items?}
    C -->|Yes| D[content-<br/>visibility]
    C -->|No| E[Search +<br/>virtualizer]
    B -->|No| F{Same<br/>height?}
    F -->|Yes| G[Fixed-<br/>height]
    F -->|No| H{GC pauses<br/>on scroll?}
    H -->|Yes| I[Recycling<br/>pool]
    H -->|No| J[Variable-<br/>height]
